The purpose of creating a responsive website of starcraft.com is so that the site will work optimally on not only 
desktops but on all devices. Currently the site is on optimal on the desktop. If you want to use the site on a phone
you have to scroll left and right and zoom in, inorder to read and see the site. The site is mostly intended for 
gamers. For gamers who play the game starcraft or gamers who want to learn and start to play. YOu will be able to 
access their profile, find out the latest news, read forums, etc.. without having to scroll left and right and 
zooming in if you are accessing the site from a non desktop device.
